    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="http://losangeles.craigslist.org/lac/ret/6025793134.html"></div>
        </div>
Seeking dynamic, customer service driven, experienced Sales Professional, for one of our two Jewelry boutiques in Original Farmers Market at the Grove in Los Angeles. (Third and Fairfax) <br>
<br>
Looking to fill this position immediately. We offer a paid training period followed by immediate full time scheduling.<br>
<br>
We are a family business and love our craft and our work. We create our own jewelry as well as showcase other designer's work. We are very involved with our clientele and treat every job and interaction with great caring detail, as do our sales professionals. At our shop, the Sales Professional serves as an ambassador of our brand by performing but not limited to essential duties &amp; responsibilities such as, provide world class service to luxury client base, meet and exceed sales goals, meet and exceed client data capture goals, maintain visual standards, comply with all company policies and procedures and maintain an environment where all associates are treated fairly and with dignity and respect. <br>
<br>
Applicant must have adequate experience working in a fashion retail setting. Must be warm and outgoing and able to provide excellent customer service. We would like the applicant to be fashion forward in personal style, and able to make an inspiring and positive impression on our customers. Must be flexible with hours in order to satisfy a dynamic schedule of some morning shifts and some evening shifts. Must be able to work on at least one weekend day as part of the regular schedule and be flexible to work all weekend every once in a while. Must have ability to be mobile on the sales floor for extended periods of time. This is not a job for much sitting. Usage of personal devices such as phones as tablets are prohibited during work hours. Only apply for this job if you are ready to leave these devices unattended during work hours.<br>
<br>
The ideal candidate must have experience in retail sales, be highly motivated, enthusiastic and who can achieve success by being sales focused, team oriented and customer service driven. They must represent and communicate our brand and lifestyle to customers through product expertise, sales competency and by providing the highest level of customer service.<br>
<br>
Jewelry experience is a plus, but we are also open to applicants with little or no jewelry experience and are happy to teach the trade, as long as there is enthusiasm and maximum effort on their end.<br>
(Candidate MUST HAVE AT LEAST TWO YEARS other retail experience.)<br>
<br>
We offer an HOURLY BASE RATE PLUS COMMISSION commensurate with experience.<br>
Please send a resume &amp; references as a reply to this post.<br>
<br>
** Applicants will be asked if they are willing to have a background check. This is a necessary part of our hiring process.    </section>

